## Your Task

Design {{ chapter_brief.get("scene_count", 3) }} scenes for this chapter. For each scene, specify all fields in the SceneBrief schema:

- ordinal, pov_character, location, time_marker
- purpose, conflict, stakes, revelation (if any)
- emotional_turn: how the emotional state shifts
- dramatic_function: the scene's structural role
- characters_present
- prohibited_moves: what the scene must NOT do
- themes_touched, symbols_touched
- setup_links (what earlier setups this pays off)
- payoff_links (what this sets up for later)
- state_mutations: what changes after this scene (character knowledge, relationships, plot state)
- is_pivotal: true if this is a structurally critical scene

Respond with a JSON object matching the ScenePlanResponse schema.
